      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "markDefs": [],
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "b4s1",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "When Jeff and Stuart took charge, they inherited a side in League 1 and immediately set about establishing the standards that would define their reign. In their debut season, the team finished third on points — a solid foundation for what was to come.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
