      "markDefs": [],
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "b11s1",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The second season was nothing short of remarkable — a league and cup double, recording an extraordinary 70 points from 30 games. That success earned the club promotion to the Premier Division, where this past season has seen us compete strongly and lay firm foundations heading into next year. The club is in a healthy position, and that is in no small part thanks to Jeff and Stuart's hard work.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
